      "title": "SL(2,c) gravity with complex vierbein and its noncommutative extension",
      "abstract": "Arkani-Hamed N, 2003, ANN PHYS-NEW YORK, V305, P96, DOI 10.1016-S0003-4916(03)00068-X; ASHTEKAR A, 1987, PHYS REV D, V36, P1587, DOI 10.1103-PhysRevD.36.1587; Cartan E, 1981, THEORY SPINORS; CHAMSEDDINE AH, 1978, NUCL PHYS B, V136, P248, DOI 10.1016-0550-3213(78)90280-8; Chamseddine AH, 2003, PHYS LETT B, V557, P247, DOI 10.1016-S0370-2693(03)00190-4; Chamseddine AH, 2001, PHYS LETT B, V504, P33, DOI 10.1016-S0370-2693(01)00272-6; Chamseddine AH, 2003, J MATH PHYS, V44, P2534, DOI 10.1063-1.1572199; Chamseddine AH, 2001, COMMUN MATH PHYS, V218, P283, DOI 10.1007-s002200100393; DAMOUR T, 1993, PHYS REV D, V47, P1541, DOI 10.1103-PhysRevD.47.1541; Damour T, 2002, PHYS REV D, V66, DOI 10.1103-PhysRevD.66.104024; EINSTEIN A, 1946, ANN MATH, V47, P731, DOI 10.2307-1969231; Fierz M, 1939, PROC R SOC LON SER-A, V173, P0211, DOI 10.1098-rspa.1939.0140; ISHAM CJ, 1972, LETT NUOVO CIMENTO, V5, P969, DOI 10.1007-BF02798862; Jurco B., 2001, MOD PHYS LETT A, V16, P343; KIBBLE TW, 1961, J MATH PHYS, V2, P212, DOI 10.1063-1.1703702; MOFFAT JW, 1995, J MATH PHYS, V36, P3722, DOI 10.1063-1.530993; Penrose R., 1988, SPINORS SPACE TIME, V2; Schrodinger E., 1985, SPACE TIME STRUCTURE; SEIBERG N, 1998, J HIGH ENERGY PHYS; SEN A, 1981, J MATH PHYS, V22, P1718; SIEGEL W, 1993, PHYS REV D, V47, P5453, DOI 10.1103-PhysRevD.47.5453; UTIYAMA R, 1956, PHYS REV, V101, P1597, DOI 10.1103-PhysRev.101.1597; VANNIEUWENHUIZEN P, 1981, PHYS REP, V68, P189, DOI 10.1016-0370-1573(81)90157-5; Weyl H, 1952, SPACE TIME MATTER"
